'''愛德華·迈克尔·吉羅斯'''，[[英帝國官佐勳章|OBE]]（{{lang-en|Edward Michael Grylls}}，{{bd|1974年|6月7日|||catIdx=吉羅斯，贝尔}}），昵称'''贝尔'''（{{lang-en|Bear}}）、'''贝爷'''（華人网友以此称呼），[[英国|英国]]探险家、作家和电视主持人，因拍摄求生系列节目《[[荒野求生秘技|荒野求生秘技]]》闻名。毕业于英国[[伦敦大学伯贝克学院|伦敦大学伯贝克学院]]（Birkbeck, University of London）。1994到1997年间，為英國第21[[特種空勤團|特種空勤團]]成员。学习了徒手搏击、沙漠寒地等环境的作战生存技能，曾去过两次[[北非|北非]]。1996年底曾在非洲南部一次自由跳伞时背部受伤。23岁登上[[珠穆朗玛峰|珠穆朗玛峰]]，成为英国登上该峰最年轻的人。2009年7月，以35岁的年龄成为了迄今最年轻的[[英國童軍總會|英國童軍總會]][[總領袖_(英國童軍總會)|总领袖]]。

== 生平 ==
贝尔生于[[北爱尔兰|北爱尔兰]]的{{link-en|多納哈迪|Donaghadee}}，4岁时家人移居英国南端[[怀特岛郡|怀特岛郡]]的{{link-en|本布里奇|Bembridge}}<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.belfasttelegraph.co.uk/sunday-life/sunday-life-reclaims-the-celebs-with-ulster-ties-14547046.html|title=Sunday Life reclaims the celebs with Ulster ties|newspaper=[[The_Belfast_Telegraph|The Belfast Telegraph]]|date=1 November 2009|accessdate=31 August 2010|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100717045427/http://www.belfasttelegraph.co.uk/sunday-life/sunday-life-reclaims-the-celebs-with-ulster-ties-14547046.html|archivedate=2010-07-17|deadurl=no}}</ref><ref>[http://www.independent.co.uk/travel/news-and-advice/my-life-in-travel-bear-grylls-756390.html "My Life In Travel: Bear Grylls"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.independent.co.uk/travel/news-and-advice/my-life-in-travel-bear-grylls-756390.html |date=20100515145238 }} ''Independent.co.uk'', 17 April 2004</ref>。他父亲是[[英国保守党|保守党]]政治家{{tsl|en|Michael Grylls|密高·格里尔斯爵士}}，母亲莎拉·格里尔斯（Lady Sarah Grylls）<ref>[http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/obituaries/1322322/Sir-Michael-Grylls.html "Obituary: Sir Michael Grylls"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/obituaries/1322322/Sir-Michael-Grylls.html |date=20141030125701 }} ''Telegraph.co.uk'', 13 February 2001</ref>也出生于政治世家<ref name="thepeerage">{{cite web |url=http://www.thepeerage.com/p24749.htm#i247489 |title=Person Page 24749 |work=thePeerage.com |accessdate=14 July 2008 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080725073715/http://www.thepeerage.com/p24749.htm#i247489 |archivedate=2008-07-25 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。贝尔有一个姐姐Lara Fawcett，她后来成为一名[[网球|网球]]教练，'Bear' 这个称号就是姐姐Lara在贝尔一周大的时候给他起的<ref>{{cite news|title=Leading questions: Bear Grylls, chief Scout|url=http://www.guardian.co.uk/society/2011/jan/12/bear-grylls-scout-association-chief-scout|work=The Guardian|location=London|date=12 January 2011|first=Jane|last=Dudman|accessdate=2014-08-08|archive-date=2012-06-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120616014150/http://www.guardian.co.uk/society/2011/jan/12/bear-grylls-scout-association-chief-scout|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

格里尔斯从小就喜爱与父亲一起[[登山|登山]]、[[航海|航海]]，并学会了[[跳伞|跳伞]]和[[自由搏击|搏击]]项目。他会说[[英语|英语]]、[[西班牙语|西班牙语]]和[[法语|法语]]<ref name="BGask">[http://www.beargrylls.com/index.php/ask-bear/ "Ask Bear Your Questions"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.beargrylls.com/index.php/ask-bear/ |date=20140602080926 }} ''BearGrylls.com''</ref>，作为一名[[基督徒|基督徒]]，他认为[[信仰|信仰]]是他生命中的重要支柱。<ref>{{cite web |url= http://www.alphausa.org/Groups/1000047564/Alpha_and_Bear.aspx |title= Three Videos Featuring Bear Grylls |work= Alpha USA |access-date= 2014-08-08 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20150222235933/http://www.alphausa.org/Groups/1000047564/Alpha_and_Bear.aspx |archive-date= 2015-02-22 |dead-url= yes }}</ref>

2000年，他与 Shara Cannings Knight 结婚<ref name="mensvogue p2">{{cite web |url=http://www.mensvogue.com/arts/articles/2007/08/grylls?currentPage=2 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080316130106/http://www.mensvogue.com/arts/articles/2007/08/grylls?currentPage=2 |archivedate=2008-03-16 |title=Out of the Wild: Bear Grylls survives the urban jungle |work=mensvogue.com |accessdate=14 July 2008 |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref name="thepeerage"/>，两人育有三个儿子：Jesse、Marmaduke<ref name="BGbiog">{{cite web|title=Biography|url=http://www.beargrylls.com/index.php/about/about-bear/|work=BearGrylls.com|accessdate=7 February 2012|archive-date=2012-02-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120205145327/http://www.beargrylls.com/index.php/about/about-bear/|dead-url=yes}}</ref>和 Huckleberry<ref name="celebrity-babies.com"/>。

格里尔斯於2019年壽辰授勳頒獎典禮上獲頒[[大英帝國勳章|大英帝國勳章]]。<ref>{{London Gazette|issue=62666|supp=y|page=B12|date=8 June 2019}}</ref>

